</header>
<div class="container-fluid evote-statement">

  <div class="row py-3">
    <div class="col-8 col-sm-6 mx-auto text-center">
      <h5 class="text-uppercase font-weight-bold">Electronic Voting System</h5>
      <p>A secured voting system that provides realtime result.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-11 col-sm-6 col-lg-4 mx-auto text-center">
